Forsyth Street, west side, south from, but not including Stanton Street. Also shown is the west side of Chrystie Street, (right) south from Rivington to Delancey Streets. Building shown in the center of clearance, is Liby's Hotel (Delancey Street, at the N.E. corner of Chrystie Street).
July 23, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, slightly southward (Rivington Street), and showing a closer
view of Libby's Hotel.
July 23, 1930.
